data.value: Shrew Soft VPN Client is an open source VPN client widely used in place of the old Cisco VPN client. Here at MTI we use it for customer sites such as Gold Band Taxis, Premier Cabs, Silvertop Taxis and Swan Taxis. By clicking next you agree to install this, otherwise if you already have this installed, click skip.
